Using  Skysphere:
	Add the BP_Sky_Sphere
	- scale it properly and set sun height and brightness

UI main menus:
	- Create a new level for the main menus
	- Create a new IU widget blueprint
	- Add all pertinent  UI elements inside this widget. 
	- You can override the onClick event to cause the interactions to take effects.
	
Adding controls to start game:
	in the main menu event graph:
		- get Player controller
		- add the custom event that the widget is ready
		- and get whatever button is necessary to take action in ui menu
		- attach an onClick(from button widget) even to execute open level
			- This level should be for your main game level, or next splash/load screen